Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.01,0:02:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Luffy and Nami were stranded at God's Shrine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.44,0:02:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eneru's ship is too far from the top of this vine. \NWhat should we do?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.98,0:02:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How can we get there?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.23,0:02:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't there some way?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.03,0:02:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the meantime, Eneru had \Nfinally found the golden bell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.74,0:02:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is it...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.04,0:02:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Splendid!!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.00,0:02:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the grand belfry that was the pride of the legendary city, Shandora!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.80,0:02:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nami, who had devised a plan, \Nsent a message to Usopp and the others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.89,0:02:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? There's something written on it.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.19,0:02:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"Cut down this huge vine so \Nit falls towards the west."
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.99,0:02:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, Eneru's final attack was imminent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.41,0:03:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've accomplished all my objectives.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.39,0:03:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left now is...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.25,0:03:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...to destroy this land together with the \Ncumuloregalis clouds using Raigo,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.34,0:03:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and set off for the Endless Vearth.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.27,0:03:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Reject!!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.65,0:03:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Break! Giant Jack!!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.24,0:03:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes! Get on, Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.29,0:03:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Run it at full power!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.92,0:03:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.97,0:04:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's insolent of you to try and come to me! \NYou need to be taught a lesson!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.64,0:04:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mamaragan!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.57,0:04:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Upper Yard is... being pulverized.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.25,0:04:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!! Nami!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.09,0:04:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like he doesn't want to come in \Ncontact with you ever again, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.18,0:04:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance!!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.76,0:04:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The ruins are being exposed!!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.65,0:04:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He intends to pulverize the ground.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.02,0:04:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wyper's lying on the ground down there!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.19,0:05:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro, too! That son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.91,0:05:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The ruins...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.92,0:05:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless, Eneru.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.88,0:05:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't bring down...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.72,0:05:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wyper!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.10,0:05:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...the history of the proud warriors who lived in the land of Shandora.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.78,0:05:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter where it is, this grand \Npower is strong, creates and nurtures.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.45,0:05:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You just can't bring it down!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.75,0:05:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many forests you burn...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.79,0:06:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many ruins you destroy...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.19,0:06:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The land won't be beaten!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.49,0:06:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of there, Wyper!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.50,0:06:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.08,0:06:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wyper's gonna die! Let me go, stupid!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.67,0:06:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? I can still hear driveling from below.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.46,0:07:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vearth is... That's right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.02,0:07:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not sinking!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.23,0:07:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Upper Yard wasn't affected at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.03,0:07:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What great power!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.53,0:07:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right. Vearth is so grand!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.67,0:08:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vearth wasn't something to fight over,{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.09,0:08:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but the blood of many people was shed, \Nand many lives were lost.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.05,0:08:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why didn't we notice it for 400 years?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.35,0:08:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wyper!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.44,0:08:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wyper!!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.57,0:08:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out! The vine is falling! \NCome over here, now!!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.78,0:08:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Go...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.21,0:08:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Straw Hat!!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.63,0:08:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come!! Eneru!!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.93,0:08:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They're a bunch of...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.29,0:08:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand over... the golden bell!!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.06,0:09:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough of this! I'm sick of you!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.48,0:09:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is big enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.28,0:09:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Disappear with the land!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.49,0:09:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Raigo!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.89,0:09:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami, thanks!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.81,0:09:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.06,0:09:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'll let your help go to waste!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.14,0:09:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Luffy!!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.56,0:09:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship is that way!!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.03,0:09:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! \NThere's an eddy of air and lightning in there!!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.28,0:09:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows what'll happen to you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.04,0:10:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you do before this huge power, rubber man?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.96,0:10:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.13,0:10:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...Fi... re... works!!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.64,0:11:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Peony!!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.11,0:11:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you use thunder to create bad \Nweather for the idyllic sky islands?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.00,0:11:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You lightning freak!!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.96,0:11:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is this abnormal electric discharge?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.38,0:11:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right...! He has gold, which can \Ntransmit electricity, on his hand!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.10,0:11:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, all I have to do is drop it before the electricity completely discharges!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.23,0:11:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything... be gone!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.87,0:12:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain McKinley! Please stop. \NThis is God's Land. It's pointless!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.70,0:12:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if there's no point!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.54,0:12:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing else humans can do when the situation is life or death!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.13,0:12:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In order to survive, \Nwe chose to abandon our land.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.72,0:12:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now we've lost a place to \Nreturn to and our way forward.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.06,0:12:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All that we can do is pray.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.85,0:12:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When we hear the "island's singing voice," \Nthis battle will end.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.11,0:12:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if no one will survive at this point...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.24,0:12:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if, had I had the \Ncourage to stand up to Eneru,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.92,0:12:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have had to involve those people...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.25,0:12:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Suu...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.38,0:13:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if God exists?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.51,0:13:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If he does, I wonder if he'd save us...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.14,0:13:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... if you really exist...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.98,0:13:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...please protect them! God!!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.57,0:13:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... make a miracle happen! \NProtect this land! God!!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.00,0:13:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear up!!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.12,0:14:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear up!!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.98,0:14:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The mass of thunderclouds has disappeared!!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.65,0:14:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.66,0:14:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.80,0:15:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.06,0:15:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat! Ring the "fire of Shandora"!!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.57,0:15:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Luffy!!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.82,0:15:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us hear the singing voice of the island!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.83,0:15:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you destroy Raigo?! \NYou monkey from the Blue Sea!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.88,0:15:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll ring you as well!!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.22,0:15:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You insolent brat!!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.51,0:15:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,200 Million Volt...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.44,0:16:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...Amaru!!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.49,0:16:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.74,0:16:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ring, you said?! You mean the golden bell?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.95,0:16:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The next time it rings, \Nit will be the end of the battle.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.70,0:16:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to hang onto such a legend?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.69,0:16:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I am God!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.30,0:16:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You are just a Paramecia!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.20,0:16:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that I can't crush \Nyou with my Logia power!!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.24,0:16:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I said it doesn't work on me!!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.11,0:16:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of this "I'm God" crap!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.76,0:16:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What god wouldn't save anything at all?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.59,0:17:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.43,0:17:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You grabbed hold of it to \Navoid being skewered, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.60,0:17:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.60,0:17:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ow, ow, it's hot! Ouch!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.65,0:17:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do, rubber man?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.31,0:17:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nowhere to escape!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.94,0:17:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The pull of your arm will make the \Nspear dig deeper and deeper into you!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.06,0:17:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet, if you get away, you'll fall!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.66,0:17:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done well to climb up this high!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.76,0:17:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,However, this is the end of \Nyou and this land, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.46,0:17:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I can create another Raigo!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.51,0:17:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our citizens' duty... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.03,0:18:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy... are the sky islands... \Ngoing to disappear?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.96,0:18:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So you chose to fall!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.01,0:18:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.63,0:18:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami! Out of the way!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.10,0:18:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What're you...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.81,0:18:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with me, earlobes!!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.81,0:18:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum... Rocket!!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.20,0:18:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.29,0:19:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying again?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.16,0:19:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the bell rings!!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.63,0:19:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'll skewer you!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.88,0:19:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Rifle!!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.13,0:19:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's too fast!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.41,0:19:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When you return to Jaya, what will you \Nthink when you see we're gone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.09,0:19:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hold on a little longer! I'll let you know...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.13,0:19:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...that "we are here"!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.22,0:20:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Light the fire of Shandora!!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.86,0:20:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been 400 years since \Nthe battle in the sky started.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.28,0:20:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Just once, we wanted to...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.99,0:20:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right. The sacred ground will...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.20,0:20:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...sing again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.59,0:20:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...someday, for sure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.19,0:20:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Six years ago, I saw a giant city of gold \Non the Grand Line island of Jaya!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.82,0:21:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The city of gold does exist!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.87,0:21:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No one in history's ever disproved \Nthe city of gold or the sky island.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.51,0:21:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what romanticism is!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.26,0:21:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Reach!!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.06,0:21:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Old guy! Can you hear it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.02,0:21:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The city of gold is here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.19,0:21:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For 400 years, the city of gold \Nhas been here all this time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.57,0:21:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...in the sky!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:11.37,0:23:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear the bell. This is romanticism!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:14.68,0:23:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the story was a meaningless \Nfantasy and I'd forgotten about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:17.67,0:23:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is only one bell in this \Nworld that echoes this much.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:20.80,0:23:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The city of gold was in the sky!
